              <span class="text-[#10A37F] text-sm font-bold">G</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-foreground">ChatGPT</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Settings &rarr; Data Controls &rarr; Export Data. Unzip and point reclaw at <code class="font-mono text-xs text-amber-400">conversations.json</code>.
          </p>
