            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-foreground">Claude</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Settings &rarr; Account &rarr; Export Data. Includes both <code class="font-mono text-xs text-amber-400">conversations.json</code> and <code class="font-mono text-xs text-amber-400">memories.json</code>.
          </p>
